Pulse 2 3.3.0
=============
 * [BUGFIX]  Allow to disable backuppc 
 * [BUGFIX]  Enhance systemd support in pulse2-setup
 * [FEATURE] Add Multicast support

Pulse 2 1.3.0
=============

 * The new imaging module allows bare-metal backup and recovery under
   Windows or GNU/Linux
 * Profile system for computers
 * New features in the MMC web interface for our native	inventory backend
 * Support for GLPI backend version 0.72.x and latest 0.78 version
 * More details at http://pulse2.mandriva.org/milestone/1.3.0
